headline: How Investors Are Reacting To Agilent Technologies (A) Raising 2026 Outlook Amid Robust Revenue Growth
summary: Agilent Technologies recently reported strong fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 results, delivering robust organic revenue growth and providing positive earnings guidance for fiscal 2026 in the range of US$7.3 billion to US$7.4 billion. A particularly material insight is Agilent’s continued momentum in core markets such as pharmaceuticals and biotech, with growth driven by new product innovation and operational efficiency improvements, even despite challenges in China and increased tax...
